      "writtenOn": "2020-12-02T04:39:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, it\u0027s possible that files written by services might conflict with files written by tests. But it aligns the status quo of existing support libraries --- a support library may write arbitrary files to output with testing.ContextOutDir, and it may overwrite files written by tests. We expect both support libraries and gRPC services to use unique names to avoid possible file name conflicts.",
      "parentUuid": "e9b0bf00_06611260",
      "revId": "0e64f732710da00ae6e3dc046591abcd17201cf7",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
